column5: Does anyone know the phone number with area code for the bait shop in Selkirk? I seem to have lost his card. Would like to hear a report as well. Thanks
Not sure who the bait shop is in Selkirk? In Winnipeg, Pro Am Tackle is 204-668-3245 In Selkirk, maybe you could call Stu Mckay at Cat's on the Red - 204-757-9876.
